name: Artist: 藤ちょこ（藤原） | Fujichoko artist's painting style
description:
藤ちょこ Style LoRA

中文 | English

--

仿藤ちょこ的作画风格的LoRA模型。

权重建议值：1 (or 0.5~1.4)

基于模型：Anything-5RE

训练信息：筛选出共计542张原画（含裁剪图），迭代1084步，多分辨率智能定向训练。

其他的一些建议：EasyNegative。此外，万一畸形四肢换个种子重画就行。

--

A LoRA model that mimics the painting style of Fujichoko.

Recommended weight value: 1 (or 0.5~1.4)

Based on model: Anything-5RE

Training information: Selected a total of 542 original images (including cropped versions), with 1084 iterations and intelligent multi-resolution training.

Some other suggestions: EasyNegative. Also, if there are any abnormal limbs, redraw them with a different seed.
